This project automates the Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) process and identifies outliers in datasets using the IQR (Interquartile Range) method. It provides quick statistical summaries, visualizations, and insights to help data scientists and analysts understand data distributions, detect anomalies, and make better business decisions.

